## 💼 10. Placement Office & Career Development Centre (CDC)

Placements and internships at VIT-AP are facilitated by the **Career Development Centre (CDC)**. Placement processes are centralized or conducted in coordination with all VIT campuses.

*   **Dream & Super Dream Offers:**
    *   *Dream Offers:* Placement packages above **₹5.5 Lakhs Per Annum (LPA)**.
    *   *Super Dream Offers:* Placement packages above **₹10 Lakhs Per Annum (LPA)**.
*   **Internships:** Many companies offer pre-placement offers (PPOs) to students during their 3rd/4th-year industrial training internships.
*   **Placement Strategy (Reddit Seniors Advice):**
    *   Maintain a CGPA above **8.5** to clear initial screening rounds for premium companies.
    *   Develop **2 to 3 solid, deployment-ready projects** (typically through SCOPE Engineering Clinics or URE).
    *   Master Data Structures & Algorithms (DSA) on competitive platforms (LeetCode, HackerRank) starting from the sophomore year to clear core coding evaluations.
